step.tex:
\begin{align}
  f(x)&=x^2-x+1 \\
  \implies f'(x)&= 2x - 1 \\
  \implies f'(x)=0&\text{ when }x=\frac{1}{2}
\end{align}
\\ \text{As }x=\frac{1}{2}\in \left(-1,1\right), f'(x) = 0\text{ somewhere in}\\
\text{the given interval }\implies f(x)\text{ is strictly }\\
\text{nothing in }\left(-1,1\right).
